the line between inside and out, offering framed views of the surrounding garden spaces and letting in natural light throughout the day. A pergola by the lap pool act as outdoor living room, tailored for relaxation and gathering.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-260625-722-05.jpg\" alt=\"Native plantings, curated garden views, and layered outdoor spaces, like this pergola and lap pool, extend the home’s living area into the landscape with effortless grace.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-260625-722-05.jpg 1200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-260625-722-05-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-260625-722-05-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-260625-722-05-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-06.jpg\" alt=\"Native plantings, curated garden views, and layered outdoor spaces, like this pergola and lap pool, extend the home’s living area into the landscape with effortless grace.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-06.jpg 1200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-06-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-06-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-06-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-06-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-07.jpg\" alt=\"Native plantings, curated garden views, and layered outdoor spaces, like this pergola and lap pool, extend the home’s living area into the landscape with effortless grace.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-07.jpg 1200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-07-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-07-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-07-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-design-landcaping-water-feature-260625-722-07-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA breezeway entrance feels equal parts welcoming and intentional, with its light wood beams, soft stonework, pivoting glass doors, and clean-lined architecture drawing your eye straight through to the landscape beyond.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/pivoting-glass-door-260625-720-01.jpg\" alt=\"A breezeway entrance feels equal parts welcoming and intentional, with its light wood beams, soft stonework, pivoting glass doors, and clean-lined architecture drawing your eye straight through to the landscape beyond.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/pivoting-glass-door-260625-720-01.jpg 1200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/pivoting-glass-door-260625-720-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/pivoting-glass-door-260625-720-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/pivoting-glass-door-260625-720-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/pivoting-glass-door-260625-720-01-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eInside, wide-plank white oak flooring and millwork introduce a soft, organic character that echoes the surrounding landscape. The living room sits at the core of the home, offering a central space for gathering without overpowering the calm tone of the interiors. Its clean lines and restrained palette let the natural materials speak for themselves.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-kitchen-banquette-260625-718-01.jpg\" alt=\"A softly lit living room with a fireplace, has been designed with natural textures.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-kitchen-banquette-260625-718-01.jpg 1200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-kitchen-banquette-260625-718-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-kitchen-banquette-260625-718-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/living-room-kitchen-banquette-260625-718-01-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe dining area is anchored by a custom banquette that wraps beneath large windows, offering a more intimate alternative to traditional seating. Its built-in design reflects the home’s emphasis on subtle Southern charm and everyday comfort, creating a natural place to pause and connect.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/curved-dining-banquette-260625-717-01.jpg\" alt=\"A custom dining banquette framed by garden views offers a relaxed, built-in space to gather, equal parts elegant and everyday.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/curved-dining-banquette-260625-717-01.jpg 1200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/curved-dining-banquette-260625-717-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/curved-dining-banquette-260625-717-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/curved-dining-banquette-260625-717-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/curved-dining-banquette-260625-717-01-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eMinimal yet warm, the kitchen balances simplicity with utility. Carefully detailed cabinetry and subtle material choices support the overall continuity of the home, while the open plan encourages an easy flow between cooking, dining, and outdoor living.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/barn-inspired-home-kitchen-design-260625-716-01.jpg\" alt=\"Warm wood tones and minimalist cabinetry define 