ound comfort.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/outdoor-fireplace-260625-718-02.jpg 1200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/outdoor-fireplace-260625-718-02-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/outdoor-fireplace-260625-718-02-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/outdoor-fireplace-260625-718-02-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003ePositioned for privacy and quiet, one of the bedrooms reflects the home’s overall tone of understated luxury. Large windows bring in soft natural light and frame views of the landscape, while layered textures create a serene atmosphere.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-design-260625-718-01.jpg\" alt=\"In this contemporary bedroom, large windows bring in soft natural light and frame views of the landscape, while layered textures create a serene atmosphere.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-design-260625-718-01.jpg 1200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-design-260625-718-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-design-260625-718-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/contemporary-bedroom-design-260625-718-01-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eRooted in heritage and designed for lasting comfort, this Sun Valley retreat is a timeless blend of beauty, function, and ease.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.gabeborder.com/\"\u003eGabe Border\u003c/a\u003e | Arch